7 §422. Registration of agents
8 A.(1) An individual shall not act as an athlete agent shall register in this
9 state unless the individual is registered with the division as provided in this
10 Chapter before the athlete agent may contact an athlete.
11 (2) An athlete agent must first be certified by the appropriate professional
